dc_title_s: Land Use Fond du Lac County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents land use for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This file folder contains the land use information for Fond du Lac County. Updated MPO area from 2018 ortho flight.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. [Data have been coded and modified to match ECWRPC Digital Map Data Standards. To obtain a copy, contact the Distributor listed under Distribution Information.]
